Package concurrency.project.ca.cellsandgrids

Class Summary
Cell Class that represent a cell inside the main Grid
CellGrid Add functionalities to the Grid.
CellGridDisplay Class that handle the visual state of the grid, repainting when necessary.
CellThread Implements the thread that will simulate the continuous execution of the steps of the automatas.
Coordinate Coordinate object: (x,y) and related operations
Grid The Grid, composed by Cell objects, with methods to manipulate and get informations.
GridDisplay A wrapper for the Grid useful to display the Grid in the GUI.
SubGridCalculation The Runnable object that is responsible to update the Grid Cells with the next state.
